---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Fitscape Terms of Use - Coe Code" description="Terms of use for Fitscape - the RPG fitness tracking app that transforms your health journey into an epic adventure.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-16">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
        <span class="text-yellow-400">Fitscape</span> Terms of <span class="text-blue-400">Use</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your epic fitness adventure starts here. Please read these terms carefully before embarking on your journey.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Terms Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-8 mb-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60 mb-6">Last updated: January 2025</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-8 text-white/80">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Welcome to Fitscape</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Welcome to Fitscape, the RPG fitness tracking app that transforms your health journey into an epic adventure. 
              These Terms of Use ("Terms") govern your use of the Fitscape mobile application and related services 
              (collectively, the "Service") provided by Coe Code LLC ("we," "us," or "our").
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">
              By downloading, installing, or using Fitscape, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree 
              to these Terms, please do not use the Service.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">App Description and Features</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Fitscape is an iOS application that gamifies health and fitness by integrating with Apple HealthKit 
              to transform your real-world activities into RPG gameplay elements:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li><strong>Character Progression:</strong> Level up stats (Strength, Constitution, Dexterity, Intelligence, Wisdom, Charisma) through real exercise</li>
              <li><strong>Dungeon Exploration:</strong> Discover and conquer dungeons through real-world movement (every 400m)</li>
              <li><strong>Equipment System:</strong> Earn gear with varying rarities through gameplay achievements</li>
              <li><strong>Quest System:</strong> Complete daily and weekly challenges based on your fitness goals</li>
              <li><strong>Social Features:</strong> Connect with friends, join guilds, and compete on leaderboards</li>
              <li><strong>Stamina System:</strong> Recovery based on sleep quality and duration</li>
              <li><strong>Health Integration:</strong> Comprehensive metrics including steps, workouts, sleep, and heart rate</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">User Eligibility and Account Requirements</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-green-400">Age Requirements</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              You must be at least 17 years old to use Fitscape. The app requires access to health data and contains 
              features designed for adult users.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-400">Account Creation</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>You must provide accurate and complete information when creating your account</li>
              <li>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials</li>
              <li>You must have a compatible iOS device (iOS 17.0 or later)</li>
              <li>Each user may only maintain one account</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-purple-400">Health Data Requirements</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Fitscape requires access to Apple HealthKit to function properly. You must grant appropriate permissions 
              for health data access including steps, workouts, sleep, and heart rate data.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Health Data Usage and Medical Disclaimers</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-red-400">Not Medical Advice</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              <strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> Fitscape is for entertainment and fitness motivation purposes only. It is not 
              intended to provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. The app's features, recommendations, and 
              insights should not replace professional medical advice.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-yellow-400">Health Data Processing</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Your health data is processed locally on your device using Apple's HealthKit framework</li>
              <li>Only computed game values (not raw health data) are synchronized with our servers</li>
              <li>You can revoke health data access at any time through iOS Settings</li>
              <li>We do not provide health recommendations or medical guidance</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-orange-400">Use at Your Own Risk</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              By using Fitscape, you acknowledge that physical exercise and activity carry inherent risks. 
              Consult with a healthcare professional before beginning any fitness program. We are not responsible 
              for injuries or health issues that may result from using the app.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">User Conduct and Community Guidelines</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-green-400">Acceptable Use</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">You agree to use Fitscape responsibly and in accordance with these guidelines:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Use the app for personal fitness motivation and entertainment</li>
              <li>Respect other users in social features and interactions</li>
              <li>Provide accurate information about your fitness activities</li>
              <li>Report bugs and provide constructive feedback</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-red-400">Prohibited Activities</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Cheating, hacking, or manipulating game mechanics</li>
              <li>Using automated systems or bots to generate false activity data</li>
              <li>Sharing inappropriate content or engaging in harassment</li>
              <li>Attempting to reverse engineer or modify the app</li>
              <li>Violating any applicable laws or regulations</li>
              <li>Interfering with other users' experience or app functionality</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-400">Social Features</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              When using guilds, friend connections, and leaderboards, you agree to maintain a respectful and 
              supportive community environment. Harassment, bullying, or inappropriate behavior may result in 
              account suspension or termination.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Beta Program Terms</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-purple-400">Beta Access</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              If you participate in the Fitscape beta program, additional terms apply:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Beta software is provided "as-is" and may contain bugs or incomplete features</li>
              <li>Your beta access may be terminated at any time without notice</li>
              <li>Beta data may be reset or lost during updates</li>
              <li>You agree to provide feedback and report issues</li>
              <li>Beta features are confidential and should not be shared publicly</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-green-400">Feedback and Testing</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              By participating in the beta program, you grant us the right to use your feedback, suggestions, 
              and bug reports to improve Fitscape without compensation or attribution.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">In-App Purchases and Subscriptions</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-yellow-400">Premium Features</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Fitscape may offer premium features through in-app purchases or subscriptions:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>All purchases are processed through the Apple App Store</li>
              <li>Prices are subject to change with notice</li>
              <li>Subscriptions auto-renew unless cancelled</li>
              <li>Refunds are handled according to Apple's refund policy</li>
              <li>Premium features may include additional equipment, customization options, or advanced analytics</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-orange-400">Payment Terms</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Payment for premium features is due immediately upon purchase. You are responsible for all charges 
              associated with your account, including those made by authorized users.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-400">Our Rights</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Fitscape and all related content, including but not limited to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Software code and algorithms</li>
              <li>Pixel art, graphics, and animations</li>
              <li>Chiptune music and sound effects</li>
              <li>Game mechanics and systems</li>
              <li>User interface designs</li>
              <li>Character designs and equipment artwork</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              All content is owned by Coe Code LLC and protected by copyright, trademark, and other intellectual 
              property laws.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-green-400">Your Rights</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              You retain ownership of your personal data and user-generated content. By using Fitscape, you grant 
              us a limited license to use your data solely for providing and improving the service.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Service Availability and Modifications</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-purple-400">Service Availability</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We strive to provide reliable service, but cannot guarantee uninterrupted availability:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>Service may be temporarily unavailable for maintenance or updates</li>
              <li>We do not guarantee compatibility with all devices or iOS versions</li>
              <li>Internet connectivity is required for certain features</li>
              <li>Third-party services (Apple Health, Firebase) may affect functionality</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-400">Modifications</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any aspect of Fitscape at any time. 
              We will provide reasonable notice of significant changes when possible.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Account Termination</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-red-400">Termination by You</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>You may delete your account at any time through the app settings</li>
              <li>Deleting your account will permanently remove all associated data</li>
              <li>Uninstalling the app does not automatically delete your account</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-orange-400">Termination by Us</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              We may suspend or terminate your account for violations of these Terms, including:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Cheating or manipulating game mechanics</li>
              <li>Harassment or inappropriate behavior</li>
              <li>Violation of community guidelines</li>
              <li>Fraudulent activity or chargebacks</li>
              <li>Extended inactivity (after 2 years)</li>
            </ul>
