              In such cases, our liability is limited to the extent permitted by applicable law.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Your privacy is important to us. Please review our Privacy Policy for detailed information about 
              how we collect, use, and protect your personal and health data. The Privacy Policy is incorporated 
              into these Terms by reference.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Governing Law and Disputes</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-400">Governing Law</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Montana, United States, without regard to 
              conflict of law principles.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-green-400">Dispute Resolution</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of Fitscape will be resolved through:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Good faith negotiation between the parties</li>
              <li>Binding arbitration if negotiation fails</li>
              <li>Arbitration conducted in Missoula, Montana</li>
              <li>Class action lawsuits are waived</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Changes to Terms</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              We may update these Terms from time to time to reflect changes in our service or legal requirements. 
              Material changes will be communicated through the app or email. Your continued use of Fitscape after 
              changes constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              If you have questions about these Terms or need support, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-4 border border-white/10">
              <p><strong>General Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@coecode.io" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">support@coecode.io</a></p>
              <p><strong>Legal Questions:</strong> <a href="mailto:legal@coecode.io" class="text-green-400 hover:text-green-300">legal@coecode.io</a></p>
              <p><strong>Privacy Concerns:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@coecode.io" class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">privacy@coecode.io</a></p>
              <p><strong>Address:</strong> Coe Code LLC, Missoula, Montana, USA</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-900/20 to-green-900/20 border border-yellow-400/30 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-yellow-400">🎮 Ready to Begin Your Adventure?</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              By using Fitscape, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms of Use. 
              Now go forth and transform your fitness journey into an epic RPG adventure!
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/60 italic">
              May your stats be high and your stamina never run out. 🗡️⚔️🏆
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation Links -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
      <a 
        href="/fitscape" 
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Back to Fitscape
      </a>
      <a 
        href="/fitscape/privacy" 
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Privacy Policy
      </a>
      <a 
        href="/connect" 
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
